OL,3,CFive police officers sacked over
OL,4,Coffensive WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FFive West Yorkshire Police officers
OL,7,Fhave been sacked over what the force
OL,8,Fcalled "inappropriate, offensive and
OL,9,Fderogatory" messages in a WhatsApp
OL,10,Fgroup.
OL,12,FA gross misconduct hearing was told
OL,13,Fthe posts included pictures from the
OL,14,Fscene of a sudden death, misogynistic
OL,15,Fand transphobic comments, as well as
OL,16,Finappropriate comments about suicide.
OL,18,FThere were also messages about sexual
OL,19,Fharassment and images of missing
OL,20,Fpeople and those who had been arrested.
