OL,6,FIn addition to the five officers
OL,7,Fdismissed, the panel ruled a further
OL,8,Fthree officers would have also been
OL,9,Fsacked had they not already resigned.
OL,11,FAll eight - PC Luke Riddett, Ex-PC Tom
OL,12,FHarrison, PC X (who is subject of an
OL,13,Fanonymity order), PS Mark Otter, PC
OL,14,FJavaid Habeeb, Ex-PC Matthew Harrison,
OL,15,FPC Dominique Hawkins and Ex-PC Lee
OL,16,FHillyard - will now be added to the
OL,17,FCollege of Policing's Barred List
OL,18,Fpreventing them from being employed in
OL,19,Fpolicing.
