OL,4,Coffensive WhatsApp messages
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent Tanya
OL,7,FWilkins said: "This misconduct hearing
OL,8,Flooked not only at the actions of this
OL,9,Fgroup but also their inaction. The
OL,10,Flack of challenge and complicity of a
OL,11,Fsupervisor being involved in these
OL,12,Fconversations has allowed a culture of
OL,13,Froutine misogyny, casual racism and
OL,14,Fbullying to develop within this team.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
